---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
const lang = 'en';
---

<Layout title="Privacy" lang={lang}>
  <div class="px-6 pt-10 md:px-10 lg:px-14 lg:pt-16">
    <div class="max-w-2xl">
      <h1 class="font-heading text-3xl font-bold tracking-tightish text-paper sm:text-4xl">Privacy Policy</h1>

      <div class="mt-8 space-y-8 text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-fog">
        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-paper">1. Controller</h2>
          <p class="mt-3">Adem Kocyigit, Tiefe Allee 33, 24149 Kiel · Email: 0406adem@gmail.com</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-paper">2. Hosting & server logs</h2>
          <p class="mt-3">
            This website is served statically (e.g. via Cloudflare Pages). When the site is accessed, the
            host processes technically necessary data in server log files (incl. IP address, date/time,
            page requested, browser type). The legal basis is Art. 6(1)(f) GDPR (legitimate interest in
            secure, stable operation).
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-paper">3. Cookies & tracking</h2>
          <p class="mt-3">This website sets no cookies of its own and uses no analytics or tracking tools.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-paper">4. Embedded videos (Vimeo / Google Drive)</h2>
          <p class="mt-3">
            Videos are only loaded after you actively click “Watch”. On playback, third-party content
            (Vimeo or Google) is loaded and your IP address, among other data, may be transmitted to these
            providers. Their respective privacy policies apply. No data is transmitted to these services
            before you click.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-paper">5. Contacting me</h2>
          <p class="mt-3">
            If you contact me by email or phone, your details are processed to handle your request
            (Art. 6(1)(b)/(f) GDPR) and are not shared without your consent.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-paper">6. Your rights</h2>
          <p class="mt-3">
            You have the right to access, rectification, erasure, restriction of processing, data
            portability and objection, as well as the right to lodge a complaint with a supervisory
            authority.
          </p>
        </section>

        <p class="border-t border-ink-line pt-6 text-xs text-fog/70">
          Note: This privacy policy is a template adapted to this project and should be legally reviewed
          before going live.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
